POLIOMYELITIS UPDATE (14): GLOBAL (WILD POLIOVIRUS TYPE 1 ENVIRONMENTAL SAMPLE, CIRCULATING VACCINE DERIVED POLIOVIRUS TYPE 2, CIRCULATING VACCINE DERIVED POLIOVIRUS TYPE 1)
